  8) Writing your first program
  9) Compiling your first program
  10) Running your first program

- *Reading*: Chapter 1 (*Think C*)

- *Programming assignments*:
  1. Install Google Cloud Shell on your PC, edit, compile and run
     =hello.c= program.
  2. Write "Hello, world!" program =hello2.c= with detailed comments.
  3. Be like Linus [Torvalds], write =linus.c=.

